Xfce4 is pretty usable on Nokia N900, Nexus 7 2013.

=== Installation ===
* <code>pmbootstrap init</code>
* <code>User interface: xfce4</code>
* <code>Extra packages: xf86-video-vesa mesa-egl libinput xf86-input-libinput</code>

